---
title: Hearty Tomato Braised Chicken with Seasoned Rice
description: This Italian classic is back and better than ever! Juicy chicken thighs get braised in a tomato sauce packed with delicious herbs and spices that is sure to leave you feeling strong!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hearty-tomato-braised-chicken-f177cd95.jpg
